Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.73,0:00:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the Code: Breaker\NSupreme Decision-making Body, "Eden."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.65,0:00:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You who possess superpowers\Nof a higher order than humans,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.15,0:00:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and are granted all power and authority,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.19,0:00:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,with which power,\Nyou are permitted to wipe out evil;
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.70,0:00:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,one of the six "Code: Breakers," Code 06...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.24,0:00:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.45,0:00:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite being the last one\Nto be appointed a Code: Breaker,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.29,0:00:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,you have carried out your work promptly,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.54,0:00:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and have developed enough to\Nhold your own with the other five.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.42,0:00:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be looking forward to even more out of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.63,0:00:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough of the worthless puffery.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.59,0:00:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,State your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.47,0:00:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch that tone of voice, you kept dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.43,0:00:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now, don't be like that.\NAnd Ogami, you're out of line, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.10,0:00:47.11,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"File downloading"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.98,0:00:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Tabata Shigeru, politician.\NEliminate this man.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.86,0:00:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this one involved with Hitomi, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.32,0:01:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Finding that out is the job\Nof a "kept dog," like you, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.25,0:01:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.21,0:01:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're going to get smart with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.46,0:01:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,then come speak to me in person,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.22,0:01:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,not through these junk pile puppets!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.80,0:01:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, don't get the wrong impression.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.30,0:01:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I will decide whether\Nor not I accept your requests.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.85,0:01:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not your "kept dog."\NThis is just a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.42,0:01:57.63,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why is there no final{\i}\N{\i1}piece to unravel this puzzle?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.63,0:02:04.97,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wander around the search area with dread{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.97,0:02:12.48,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With shaky self-confidence{\i}\N{\i1}facing unyielding damnation,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.48,0:02:16.32,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm still alive, but I can't catch up{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.32,0:02:22.53,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to residual images of hidden memories{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.53,0:02:26.70,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let loose dark shame unbounded{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.70,0:02:30.54,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to the ends of this world of kindness{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.54,0:02:34.63,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even hopes best forgotten are silenced{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.63,0:02:38.30,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}as corruption spreads out before our eyes{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.30,0:02:41.51,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Consign it to darkness{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.51,0:02:45.26,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}An ego on trial{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.26,0:02:56.40,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In a moment of hesitation is seen ecstasy{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.62,0:03:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I am, home again,\Nwithout knowing how...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.67,0:03:16.67,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord6\be6}"Episode 4: 'War Cry'"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.51,0:03:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura, we need to have a talk today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.22,0:03:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Sakura. This is not once,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.34,0:03:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,but twice that you were\Nsleeping out by the front gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.76,0:03:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That shows poor manners.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.60,0:03:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, my manners have been poor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.31,0:03:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened? Go ahead\Nand tell your Papa and Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.60,0:03:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.06,0:03:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-The truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.78,0:03:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,...I've joined the mountaineering club!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.45,0:03:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hence, I've been training myself regularly
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.53,0:03:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,to be able to endure sleeping outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.78,0:03:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is {\i1}that{\i} all it is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.37,0:03:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's something you'll have to work hard at!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.96,0:03:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got our support, Sakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.75,0:03:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Sakura, am off!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.05,0:04:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura was wearing her "lying face."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.26,0:04:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.34,0:04:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Good question. But then,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.81,0:04:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,whenever Sakura lies,\Nit's always for somebody else's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.98,0:04:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,She also only does\Nit when she believes it's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.40,0:04:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have faith in Sakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.69,0:04:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.78,0:04:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I am profoundly sorry,\NFather and Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.33,0:04:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.17,0:04:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning! You're Sakura, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.25,0:04:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I am. And you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.34,0:04:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Toki. I came to pick\Nyou up in Ogami's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.97,0:04:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami's place?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.35,0:04:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He botched things last night,\Nso he can't come today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.39,0:04:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He botched things? You mean his job?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.68,0:04:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep. His Code: Breaker job.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.10,0:04:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, Toki, you, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.61,0:05:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The great Toki is Code: Breaker Code 04!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.44,0:05:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami is Code 06, the lowest one,\Nso I have to look out for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.33,0:05:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a fact? So, where is Ogami now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.41,0:05:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He got chewed out by the higher-ups,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.37,0:05:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,so he's probably on\Nthe verge of tears somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.46,0:05:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Him... on the verge of tears?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.55,0:05:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.59,0:05:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, forgive me. It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.30,0:05:31.43,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Traffic Safety Week"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.01,0:05:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Toki, have you\Nbeen with Ogami for very long?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.39,0:05:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, let's see. We are close friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.14,0:05:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.06,0:05:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep. So you can ask me anything about Ogami.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.06,0:05:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you all sorts of things...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.44,0:05:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.82,0:05:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If you are his friend,\NToki, then you can tell him, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.90,0:05:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I want him to stop what he is doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.57,0:05:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You want him to stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.83,0:05:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki, you are a Code: Breaker, too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.83,0:05:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, sounds like there's a story behind this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.87,0:06:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. I'd like to hear all about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.09,0:06:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Truthfully?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.09,0:06:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we can't do it here, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.63,0:06:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We can talk anywhere;\Nit doesn't have to be here, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.51,0:06:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I have something\Nto discuss about Ogami, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.02,0:06:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.39,0:06:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's something that involves you, too, Sakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.19,0:06:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.44,0:06:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep. Something very important.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.28,0:06:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm? What is the matter, Toki?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.78,0:06:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.99,0:06:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that for, Ogami?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.91,0:06:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't listen to this guy's drivel!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.58,0:06:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,How mean, Ogami! And after\Nnot seeing each other in so long, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.29,0:06:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Ogami!\NAren't you supposed to be friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.00,0:06:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Who says we're friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.34,0:06:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.09,0:06:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We {\i1}are{\i} friends, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.97,0:06:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I've sure pounded you\Nto tears enough, haven't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.31,0:06:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to get pounded again, Ogami?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.44,0:07:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop this fighting, both of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.61,0:07:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want, Toki?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.32,0:07:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a fine how-do-you-do.\NWe have work to discuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.65,0:07:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You heard about tonight, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.07,0:07:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The higher-ups are\Nworried about you handling it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.03,0:07:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I ended up closing\Nthe deal yesterday, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.46,0:07:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That is why the great Toki\Nwound up having to accompany you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.59,0:07:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason I'm all the way\Nout here so early this morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.96,0:07:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,...is because I wanted to warn your\Nlower-rank self not to drag me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.93,0:07:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You should worry more\Nabout yourself than me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.52,0:07:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Before you find yourself Lost at\Na critical time, and drag {\i1}me{\i} down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.81,0:07:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a real pain in the ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.27,0:07:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sick of looking at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.15,0:07:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you like, we can\Nsettle things right here, Code 06!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.49,0:07:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.87,0:08:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna be sorry, Toki!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.12,0:08:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut your trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.89,0:08:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.56,0:08:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop this, the both of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.15,0:08:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Letting your fists do the\Ntalking is fine, but first, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.74,0:08:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sakura... you're hurting us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.07,0:08:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry, I didn't mean it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.58,0:08:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ee-yow...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.24,0:08:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's your own faults...\Nsuddenly going crazy on each other like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.05,0:08:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a funny one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.59,0:08:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The colors of his eyes...\Nthey're just like Fujiwara's.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.68,0:09:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Sakura?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.35,0:09:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you captivated by my good looks?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.68,0:09:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not be conceited, Toki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.77,0:09:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just looking at the\Ndifference in your eye colors.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.10,0:09:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're captivated, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.19,0:09:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later, Ogami. Hang in there at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.20,0:09:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Ogami. Tell me more about Toki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.08,0:09:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a liar. Please don't believe what he says.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.54,0:09:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're being quite hard on him.\NDid something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.47,0:09:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I think about it,\NToki mentioned your work back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.72,0:09:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you mean\Nto kill more people, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.14,0:09:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, and what did you mean by "Lost"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.31,0:09:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it have to do with your power?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.81,0:09:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Sakurakoji Sakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.61,0:09:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing on a lovely morning
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.28,0:09:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,like having a lovely ultra-teatime.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.41,0:10:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you have some with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.70,0:10:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He's having tea again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.41,0:10:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Shh, he'll hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.37,0:10:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Heike.\NWhile I appreciate your invitation,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.04,0:10:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,class is about to start,\Nso I'm afraid I must pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.30,0:10:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Well then, perhaps another time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.39,0:10:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This grammar will be on\Nthe next test, so be sure you learn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.98,0:10:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I must grill Ogami for\Nanswers during the break period.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.98,0:10:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, Aoyama,\Nread the next example sentence...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.32,0:10:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Sakurakoji?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.78,0:10:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher! I, Sakurakoji Sakura, am feeling unwell,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.66,0:10:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,so I will go visit the nurse's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.49,0:10:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Wait, Sakurakoji!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.79,0:10:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.16,0:10:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo, Sakura, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.29,0:10:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That is my question to you!\NWhat are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.75,0:10:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, you're too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.17,0:10:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And here I've come to\Nhave a look at your school.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.80,0:11:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're lying. I'll bet you're just\Nhere to rummage around again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.30,0:11:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my, how naughty of you\Nto sneak out during class, Ogami.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.23,0:11:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,There you both go again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.31,0:11:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That uniform is from some other school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.48,0:11:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Why aren't you at school?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.36,0:11:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.20,0:11:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here today to tour this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.87,0:11:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that right? Well, welcome to our school!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.12,0:11:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, he's lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.83,0:11:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Ogami, you doubt me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.12,0:11:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If you like, you can call\Nover to my school and ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.05,0:11:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That seal... I-It couldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.55,0:11:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That ultra-tough school,\Nwith a T-score of 70, and the nation's
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.30,0:11:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,highest rate of placement to Tokyo University,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.26,0:11:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,where the sons and daughters\Nof captains of industry go...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.85,0:11:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Heisei Gakuin High School?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.60,0:11:54.31,Default - Style 15,,0,0,0,,{\fad(740,0)\fscx70\be15\fs150\an8\pos(960,240)\c&H0B0B09&\3c&HD2CAC0&\b1}Most elite school in Japan
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.61,0:11:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.94,0:11:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,"Yeah, that's right" he says, passing it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.07,0:12:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I just chose it because\Nit was the closest one to my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.70,0:12:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, Toki, from Heisei Gakuin High School,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.49,0:12:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,will be sitting in with our class.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.79,0:12:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, let's all hit\Nit off and study hard together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.04,0:12:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.25,0:12:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, he's kind of handsome.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.12,0:12:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He gets high marks, coming from Hei-gaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.30,0:12:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if he's going to\Nstudy earnestly, then okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.80,0:12:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Lunch! Lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.60,0:12:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm starving!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.89,0:12:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami, come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.14,0:12:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's talk while eating lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.85,0:12:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You don't suppose Sakurakoji\Nmade those lunches herself, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.27,0:12:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- Their relationship is like {\i1}that{\i} already?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.73,0:12:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- Sakura is on fire!\N- Their relationship is like {\i1}that{\i} already?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.27,0:12:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.65,0:12:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.45,0:12:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Ogami!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.86,0:12:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki, you come, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.32,0:12:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.16,0:12:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's eat these lunches together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.83,0:12:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I've got something I need to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.75,0:12:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Just come with me! We need to talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.79,0:12:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.17,0:13:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What on earth is going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.96,0:13:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this? A love triangle, all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.63,0:13:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Lousy Ogami! Take off on me, will he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.97,0:13:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,My apologies, Toki.\NYou had something to do, but I insisted...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.31,0:13:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's all right.\NI just came to see someone's face.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.69,0:13:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone's face?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.15,0:13:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- So then, Sakura, what did you want to talk about?\N- Okay then, later on...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.15,0:13:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- How handsome!\N- Eh? Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.94,0:13:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It may not make any sense to\Ndiscuss this with you, Toki,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.99,0:13:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,but as I touched on this morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.66,0:13:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,is there no way that you can stop\NOgami from killing any more people?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.00,0:13:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts Ogami himself, as well.\NI understand not why he goes so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.58,0:13:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Code: Breakers have an objective.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.09,0:13:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,In exchange for carrying out that objective,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.18,0:13:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,we accept jobs that get our hands dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.97,0:13:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He's probably up to something, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.31,0:13:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami's objective...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.73,0:13:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, say...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.98,0:14:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,...to protect somebody, or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.91,0:14:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes me jealous\Nthat you're interested in Ogami.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.12,0:14:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura, have you ever been held here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.58,0:14:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It is indecent to touch a\Nwoman's breasts, is it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.05,0:14:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, that hurt...\NIf Sissy could do it, why can't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.13,0:14:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Sissy? Oh, then you {\i1}are{\i}\NFujiwara's brother, all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.93,0:14:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder you look so alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.52,0:14:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you know? Ogami wants\Nto eat Sakura's lunch too, doesn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.52,0:14:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ogami!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.31,0:14:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- Don't get me wrong.\N- Ogami!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.98,0:14:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,She's an idiot,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.36,0:14:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,so I'm just keeping watch to\Nmake sure you don't fool her again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.61,0:14:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I-Idiot? What do you mean, Idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.86,0:14:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.91,0:14:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Ogami!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.96,0:15:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what did you want\Nto talk about, Miss Sakurakoji?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.00,0:15:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,About you and Code: Breakers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.38,0:15:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Special friendship!\NCamaraderie that goes beyond the sexes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.34,0:15:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I see that you are concerned\Nabout Ogami. My, how considerate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.81,0:15:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? What is the matter, Miss Sakurakoji?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.98,0:15:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Judging by the look on your face,\Nyou do not wish me to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.56,0:15:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? No! That's not it at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.86,0:15:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujiwara!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.49,0:15:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi-{\i1}tan{\i0}, Mi-{\i1}tan{\i}, I'm glad you're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.28,0:15:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- I missed you! Hi-{\i1}tan{\i0}...\NMi-{\i1}tan{\i0}... Hi-{\i1}tan{\i0}... Mi-{\i1}tan...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.28,0:15:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- N-Nenene...\N- I missed you! Hi-{\i1}tan{\i0}...\NMi-{\i1}tan{\i0}... Hi-{\i1}tan{\i0}... Mi-{\i1}tan{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.78,0:15:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't look like we're\Ngoing to be able to talk today, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.79,0:15:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Sakura?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.46,0:15:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Nothing! Nothing at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.63,0:15:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Ogami, Hi-{\i1}tan{\i} and Mi-{\i1}tan{\i}\Nare all mine. You can't have them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.34,0:15:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the use? That's it for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.85,0:16:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right. Fujiwara, your younger brother is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.98,0:16:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.44,0:16:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, right over... Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.65,0:16:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.53,0:16:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura, what do you mean?\NI don't have any brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.96,0:16:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Code: Breakers, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.85,0:16:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you not to follow me, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.98,0:16:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm keeping my eye on you,\Nto make sure you do not kill again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.44,0:16:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the story with Toki and Fujiwara?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.24,0:16:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,A Code: Breaker is something\Nthat doesn't exist in this society...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.16,0:17:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,a being unknown to anyone,\Nand whose existence is utterly erased.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.37,0:17:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,To anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.41,0:17:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Even supposing Toki did have a family,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.46,0:17:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,as long as he is a Code: Breaker,\Nit's as though he didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.34,0:17:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You're kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.67,0:17:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If Sissy could do it, why can't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.05,0:17:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I just came to see someone's face.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.01,0:17:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I've got something I need to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.18,0:17:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.85,0:17:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey there. Sakura, you tagged along?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.77,0:17:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki, is Fujiwara...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.11,0:17:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? That? It's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.61,0:17:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What, did you think I was her brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.66,0:17:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You're letting Ogami\Nmake a fool of you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.29,0:17:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not untrue.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.16,0:17:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki, Fujiwara {\i1}is{\i} your older sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.13,0:17:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki, when you said "to protect somebody,"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.30,0:17:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,you were talking\Nabout Fujiwara, were you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.72,0:17:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're working as a\NCode: Breaker to protect your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.68,0:18:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a champion of justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.22,0:18:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.31,0:18:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a Code: Breaker because\NI'm a champion of justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.02,0:18:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- Toki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.81,0:18:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- For the time being...\N- Toki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.82,0:18:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'd like to be protecting Hi-{\i1}tan{\i} and Mi-{\i1}tan.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.74,0:18:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop trying to muddle the\Nsituation with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.78,0:18:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.49,0:18:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just about time. Shall we get started?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.07,0:18:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.12,0:18:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't brush me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.63,0:18:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.97,0:18:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd create a racket if\Nthe alarm went off on us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.64,0:18:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I shut down the security system.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.81,0:18:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.64,0:18:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Next up...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.15,0:19:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,W-W-What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.82,0:19:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki's special ability. He is able\Nto freely manipulate magnetism.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.74,0:19:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Special ability? Magnetism?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.96,0:19:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki's power...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.01,0:19:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! What are you planning to do here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.30,0:19:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, right?\NWe're teaching evil a lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.97,0:19:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridiculous! Here in this residential area?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.64,0:19:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like they're ready to tangle, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.10,0:19:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! They're not going to just sit quietly
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.14,0:19:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,after you've destroyed their gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.06,0:19:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Sakurakoji, please leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.36,0:19:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.73,0:19:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, let's get right to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.23,0:19:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.36,0:19:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Halt! Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.99,0:19:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take care of the targets.\NYou just stay out of my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.83,0:19:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't {\i1}you{\i} go slowing {\i1}me{\i} down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.41,0:19:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.71,0:19:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.55,0:19:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're here, are you, Code: Breakers?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.80,0:20:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you interfere.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.30,0:20:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.98,0:20:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my, aiming for the head, are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.94,0:20:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're raring to kill us, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.98,0:20:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He stopped the bullets?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.32,0:20:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Something like that is even possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.20,0:20:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,...for Code: Breakers?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.99,0:20:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Bullets mean nothing\Nin the face of my special ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.95,0:20:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Toki!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.75,0:20:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have them back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.00,0:20:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.21,0:20:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! They were trying to kill us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.22,0:20:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yeah, but...\N- Now to finish them...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.15,0:20:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.98,0:21:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,A special ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.49,0:21:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.83,0:21:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't need those good-for-nothings, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.63,0:21:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Surprised? You Code: Breakers\Naren't the only ones
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.92,0:21:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,who use special abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.06,0:21:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,They have strange powers, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.27,0:21:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This place received government orders
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.44,0:21:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,to conduct special ability research.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.52,0:21:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The government?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.73,0:21:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty ridiculous-looking research, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.83,0:22:01.55,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One day, you, too, will know{\i}\N{\i1}where that white crow is heading{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.55,0:22:07.22,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We fly through the brilliant city,{\i}\N{\i1}unnoticed by all around{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.64,0:22:21.77,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Looking only for a reason to live{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.77,0:22:27.15,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ashamed of our hollow selves{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.15,0:22:31.95,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Should we just laugh and go along{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.95,0:22:37.58,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}with the rules the world has decided on?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.58,0:22:42.34,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Stripped bare, following{\i}\N{\i1}wherever our instincts lead{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.34,0:22:46.38,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to the truth from{\i}\N{\i1}which we've averted our eyes{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.38,0:22:51.01,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Verdicts handed down for no one's sake{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.01,0:22:55.85,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cast off the dark robes and get on your feet{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.85,0:23:00.60,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pure white wishes become our wings{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.60,0:23:05.28,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shake off your hesitations now, and fly high{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.28,0:23:13.78,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Have no fear; the answers{\i}\N{\i1}lie beyond the darkness{\i}
